***** JSBOARD + OOPS administartion Center *********************************

Original Developer              : Byung Chan Kim <redhands@linux.sarang.net>
Source Disturibute              : Joung Kyun Kim <admin@oops.org>

## Warning ##

This package turned out to work in Redhat Debian FreeBSD systems.
Any one who wants install this package on any other platform
must revise it as needed for himeself/herself and must read
jsboard/README.OTHERS.OS file.

Attention : OOPS administration Center is not GPL.
            See also admin/License !

